        "font_size_title_sub": "12px",
        "color_title_sub": "",
        "des": "<p align=\"left\">Through extensive communication with our customers, we have come to realize that living in an organized manner leads to a sense of fulfillment. We firmly believe that when all the clutter is neatly arranged, it frees up space to indulge in your passions.</p><p align=\"left\">Our brand philosophy revolves around providing creative and high-quality storage furniture and solutions that help you create a well-organized and clutter-free living environment. Our goal is to offer you more space and freedom, enabling you to focus on what truly brings you joy. With every item having a proper storage location, you can easily find and utilize them without wasting time or energy.</p>",
